
@host = http://localhost:3001/api
@trick_id = 3c68ef76-c33c-4aee-ab13-871fd6da750b


### public route
GET {{host}}/ping

### authenticated
GET {{host}}/authenticated
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a trick
POST {{host}}/tricks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
content-type: application/json

{
"title": "Trick number two",
