### Get a trick
GET {{host}}/tricks/{{trick_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all tricks
GET {{host}}/tricks/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update a trick
PUT {{host}}/tricks/{{trick_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
content-type: application/json

{
"title": "Trick One Again",
"description": "The first trick ever updated",
